This ChangeLog file is no longer maintained - see the git repo history for
more recent changes: https://xapian.org/bleeding

Fri Sep 25 07:33:41 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Update.

Thu Sep 24 05:25:46 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* python/smoketest2.py: Add new testcase to catch any internal
	  functions, methods, constants, etc which have accidentally been
	  wrapped.

Thu Sep 24 03:38:17 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* xapian.i: Ignore internal methods of Xapian::Weight.

Thu Sep 24 01:28:08 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* python/Makefile.am: SWIG now automatically makes xapian.Error a
	  subclass of the Python Exception class, so drop our post-processing
	  tweak to add this in.

Thu Dec 15 12:50:42 GMT 2011  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* generic/except.i: Correct comments about how and where this file gets
	  included - this changed in the major restructuring a few months ago.
	* generic/except.i,php/except.i,tcl8/except.i: Return
	  Error::get_description() rather than get_type + ": " + get_msg().  In
	  many cases this is the same, but if context or errno are available,
	  get_description() includes them.  Catch and report std::exception
	  rather than handling it as an unknown error (so in particular
	  std::bad_alloc will now be reported more helpfully).

Sun May 24 13:30:26 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* configure.ac: Fix configure test for whether $MONO can run CSharp
	  programs - previously it would always fail, which would mean that
	  the CSharp tests wouldn't be run if CSharp programs can't be run
	  directly.

Wed May 20 09:56:51 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Another update for 1.2.21.

Tue May 19 05:45:48 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/t/symbol-test.t: If the symboltest module build fails, skip the
	  test - it's likely due to external reasons, like incompatible
	  compiler flags being taken from Perl's Config module, due to Perl
	  having been built with a different compiler to Xapian.

Mon May 18 04:48:24 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/t/symbol-test.t: Remove lingering use of @args, which is no
	  longer set.

Mon May 18 04:44:56 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Another update prior to 1.2.21 release.

Mon May 18 04:43:38 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* ruby/smoketest.rb: Extend testcase to check returned MSet size.

Fri May 15 12:36:28 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/util.i.in: Just call the existing Perl Xapian::inmemory_open()
	  function rather than defining and wrapping an inline C++
	  new3_WritableDatabase() function which calls InMemory::open().

Fri May 15 05:34:00 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Another update for 1.2.21.

Fri May 15 05:05:32 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* README: Add note about Python 3 support.

Fri May 15 04:54:37 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS,configure.ac: Update for 1.2.21.

Thu May 14 13:57:00 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* README: Remove the experimental marker from the Lua bindings.

Thu May 14 12:40:57 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* README: Remove note about the subclassing bug with PHP 5.4 and later
	  - that was fixed in 1.2.19.

Thu May 14 12:07:03 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/util.i.in: Update list of unwrapped things.

Thu May 14 11:47:46 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/Makefile.am: Perl tests are ordering-dependent, so
	  use .NOTPARALLEL to avoid problems during parallel builds.

Thu May 14 11:28:19 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/Makefile.am,perl/t/collapse.t: Add test coverage for
	  Enquire::set_collapse_key() with 1 and 2 parameters.

Thu May 14 11:25:44 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/Makefile.am,perl/t/stem.t: Add test that we can create all the
	  stemmers returned by Stem::get_available_languages().

Thu May 14 11:17:54 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/Search/Xapian/,perl/docs/examples/,
	  perl/generate-perl-exceptions,perl/t/databasemodified.t,
	  perl/t/search.t,perl/t/writabledatabase.t,perl/util.i.in: Whitespace
	  clean-up.

Thu May 14 10:57:31 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/generate-perl-exceptions: Remove superfluous ';' after closing
	  '}' of namespace.

Thu May 14 10:52:53 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/generate-perl-exceptions: Use croak_sv() or ERRSV if defined.

Thu May 14 10:32:12 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* lua/generate-lua-exceptions,perl/generate-perl-exceptions,
	  python/generate-python-exceptions: Have a single copyright statement
	  at the top of the script (in a $copyright variable), and substitute
	  this into the generated script.

Thu May 14 10:28:26 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Update.

Thu May 14 03:54:05 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/util.i.in: Wrap missing constants OP_SYNONYM and STEM_ALL_Z.

Thu May 14 03:50:37 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/util.i.in: Remove duplicate %constant for OP_VALUE_RANGE.

