	* configure.ac: Simplify test of Ruby version.

Wed May 06 07:40:59 GMT 2015  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* perl/util.i.in: Add workaround for Perl defining a seed() macro
	  which breaks '#include <algorithm>' undef C++11 with GCC.

