	* NEWS,configure.ac: Update for 1.2.17.

Sun Jan 05 22:09:31 GMT 2014  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Update.

Sun Dec 29 22:12:35 GMT 2013  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* Backport change from trunk:
	* configure.ac,generic/generic.mk: Improve workaround which allows
	  building against an uninstalled xapian-core on OS X - this should
	  now work with any uninstalled xapian-core (not only in a tree
	  with the same layout as an SVN or git checkout) and it also won't
	  try to build against "../xapian-core/.libs" just because it happens
	  to exist.  (Fixes #322)

Tue Dec 24 21:24:42 GMT 2013  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* configure.ac: Check python2 before python when probing for a python
	  interpreter for the Python 2 bindings.

Tue Dec 24 21:04:27 GMT 2013  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* configure.ac: Reject Python 3 when probing for a python interpreter
	  for the Python 2 bindings, as some distros now point /usr/bin/python
	  at Python 3, and it's better to fail with a clear message in
	  configure.

Fri Dec 20 08:04:33 GMT 2013  Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>

	* NEWS: Update.

