	* tcl/except.i: New file, overriding swig/defaults/except.i for tcl.
	* tcl/util.i: Remove exception handling stuff - moved to except.i.
	  No longer sets XAPIAN_EXCEPTION_HANDLER - presence of except.i has
	  similar effect.
